trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<system.identityModel.services>" name="<system.identityModel.services>" href=""></xref> section in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<system.identityModel.services>" name="<system.identityModel.services>" href=""> </xref> delen i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: The `<system.identityModel.services>` section configures authentication using WS-Federation protocol.
trans-unit.target: Den `<system.identityModel.services>` delen konfigurerer godkjenning ved hjelp av WS-Federation protokollen.

trans-unit.source: It contains elements that configure the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule> (WSFAM) and the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> (SAM).
trans-unit.target: Den inneholder elementer som konfigurerer den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>(WSFAM) og <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule>(SAM).</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.SessionAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>
